ky-krumlov-castle.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111607\/cesky-krumlov-castle-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111607\/cesky-krumlov-castle-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111607\/cesky-krumlov-castle-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111607\/cesky-krumlov-castle-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111607\/cesky-krumlov-castle-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111607\/cesky-krumlov-castle-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111607\/cesky-krumlov-castle-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111607\/cesky-krumlov-castle-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111607\/cesky-krumlov-castle-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111607\/cesky-krumlov-castle-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111607\/cesky-krumlov-castle-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111607\/cesky-krumlov-castle-1440x961.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111607\/cesky-krumlov-castle-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111607\/cesky-krumlov-castle.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4><strong>Castle Museum &amp; Tower<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Don&#x2019;t miss the panoramic view from the top of the castle tower; well worth climbing the 150 steps for! The tower is iconic to Cesky Krumlov.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111514\/pink-castle-tower-cesky-krumlov-guide.jpg\" alt=\"pink castle tower cesky krumlov guide\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"pink castle tower cesky krumlov guide\" class=\"wp-image-43439 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111514\/pink-castle-tower-cesky-krumlov-guide.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111514\/pink-castle-tower-cesky-krumlov-guide-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111514\/pink-castle-tower-cesky-krumlov-guide-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111514\/pink-castle-tower-cesky-krumlov-guide-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111514\/pink-castle-tower-cesky-krumlov-guide-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111514\/pink-castle-tower-cesky-krumlov-guide-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111514\/pink-castle-tower-cesky-krumlov-guide-1229x1536.jpg 1229w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111514\/pink-castle-tower-cesky-krumlov-guide-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111514\/pink-