und-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> A night, the castle is beautifully lit up and shines across the town.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>Opening Times &amp; Entry Fees<\/strong><br>Depending on the time of the year, the castle opening times, and the tours, can change. Generally though, the museum, tower, and exterior of the castle are accessible every day from 9 AM &#x2013; 5 PM. However, make sure to check the <a href=\"http:\/\/www.zamek-ceskykrumlov.cz\/en\/plan-your-visit\/opening-hours\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">official website<\/a> for more details. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111524\/castle-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-43427 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111524\/castle-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111524\/castle-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111524\/castle-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111524\/castle-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111524\/castle-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111524\/castle-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https:\/\/static.saltinourha