charming medieval part of the town, home to different colored houses. Many years ago, the servants of the castle used to live in this neighborhood. Now the area is home to cute little shops and restaurants.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also discover: <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/czech-republic\/karlovy-vary\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The Spa Town, Karlovy Vary in the Czech Republic<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111457\/cesky-krumlov-czech-republic-city-guide.jpg\" alt=\"cesky krumlov czech republic city guide\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"cesky krumlov czech republic city guide\" class=\"wp-image-43462 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111457\/cesky-krumlov-czech-republic-city-guide.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111457\/cesky-krumlov-czech-republic-city-guide-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111457\/cesky-krumlov-czech-republic-city-guide-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111457\/cesky-krumlov-czech-republic-city-guide-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111457\/cesk