r\">\n<h3>6. Monastery of the Minorites<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Within the Latran district, lies a peaceful monastery, and like everywhere else in Cesky Krumlov, is absolutely beautiful! It&#x2019;s well worth a visit, particularly for its gardens, and interior murals. Its story is slightly unusual in that at one time both monks and nuns lived here together!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hotels-cesky-krumlov\/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Here are all your hotel options in Cesky Krumlov.<\/a><\/p>\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111600\/Monastery-Minorities-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"Monastery Minorities\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Monastery Minorities\" class=\"wp-image-43383 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111600\/Monastery-Minorities-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111600\/Monastery-Minorities-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111600\/Monastery-Minorities-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111600\/Monastery-Minorities-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.salt