1w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111546\/cesky-krumlov-Monastery-Minorities-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111546\/cesky-krumlov-Monastery-Minorities-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>Opening Times &amp; Entry fee<br><\/strong>In the main spring\/summer season the monastery is open every day from 10 AM &#x2013; 6 PM. The garden is open every day from 7 AM &#x2013; 7 PM. Note that the opening times vary in the winter.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The regular entry for an adult is 150 CZK (5.70 EUR). However, if you have a Cesky Krumlov Card the monastery is included in the price.<\/p>\n\n\n\n                <div class=\"video-block__wrapper video-block__wrapper--breakout\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/VideoObject\">\n                <h3 class=\"video-block__wrapper-title\" itemprop=\"name\">Czech Republic<\/h3>\n\n                <meta itemprop=\"thumbnail\" content=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23112829\/Thumb-Czechrepublic-copy-800x450.jpg\">\n                <meta itemprop=\"description\" content=\"Czech Republic\">\n                <meta itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\" content=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23112829\/Thumb-Czechrepublic-copy-800x450.jpg\">\n                <meta itemprop=\"uploadDate\" content=\"2020-09-20 09:23:30\">\n\n\n                <div class=\"video-block video-block--mediavine\">\n                    <div class=\"video-block__embed\">\n                        <div class=\"mv-video-target mv-video-id-xrhcxc8wejhjm2ztgl0e\" data-video-id=\"xrhcxc8wejhjm2ztgl0e\" data-volume=\"70\" data-ratio=\"16:9\" data-autoinsert=\"true\" data-disable-jsonld=\"true\"><\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n\n                <a class=\"video-block__credit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/c\/saltinourhair?sub_confirmation=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"YouTube Salt in our Hair\">\n                    <div class=\"socials__item\">\n                        <span class=\"socials__link\">\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-youtube\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-youtube\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <span>Subscribe to our <b>YouTube channel<\/b> and never miss a video!<\/span>\n                <\/a>\n\n                <div class=\"video-block__bg\">\n                    <img class=\"video-block__bg-image lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23112829\/Thumb-Czechrepublic-copy-800x450.jpg\" alt=\"Czech Republic\" height=\"450\" width=\"800\">\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2>Day 2 &#x2013; Relaxing Cesky Krumlov<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Go for a completely different experience on day 2 in Cesky Krumlov. The Vltava River is a giant playground for visitors to do watersports and admire the city from the water.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111447\/vintage-photos.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-43465 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111447\/vintage-photos.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111447\/vintage-photos-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111447\/vintage-photos-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111447\/vintage-photos-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111447\/vintage-photos-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111447\/vintage-photos-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111447\/vintage-photos-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111447\/vintage-photos-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111447\/vintage-photos-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111447\/vintage-photos-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111447\/vintage-photos-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111447\/vintage-photos-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111447\/vintage-photos-1440x961.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111447\/vintage-photos-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111447\/vintage-photos.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>7. Canoe or Kayak on the Vltava River<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the best things to do in Cesky Krumlov is to paddle along the water of the Vltava River. Czech people love their watersports, and Cesky Krumlov is no exception! There are tonnes of canoe\/kayak shops where you can hire a boat, or do a guided tour, and explore the river for the day. Each shop will offer different packages, so you can make the journey as long or as short as you want. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/rafting-tour-cesky-krumlov\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book a rafting tour easily online<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111635\/Kayak-Vltava-River-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"Kayak Vltava River\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Kayak Vltava River\" class=\"wp-image-43334 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23111635\/Kayak-Vltava-River